## Rules

1. Edit and build addon code **in this repo only**.
2. Do not modify `MultiplayerChat.dll` for addon fixes unless the user explicitly approves a core release in `BeatSaber-Multiplayer-Chat`.
3. Use existing core bridges (`IMpChatHost`, etc.); do not change bridge contracts without approval.
4. Release: `dotnet build -c Release` copies DLL + manifest to `releases/Plugins/MultiplayerChat/Addons/` and the configured Beat Saber instance.
